trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<federationConfiguration>" name="<federationConfiguration>" href=""></xref> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_<federationConfiguration>" name="<federationConfiguration>" href=""> </xref> 구성 파일의 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The `<federationConfiguration>` element contains the settings that configure the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>).
trans-unit.target: `<federationConfiguration>` 요소는 WS-페더레이션 인증 모듈을 구성 하는 설정을 포함 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) 및 세션 인증 모듈 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>).</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationElement"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The `<cookieHandler>` element configures the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler> object that the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) uses to read and write cookies.
trans-unit.target: `<cookieHandler>` 요소 구성의 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler>개체를 세션 인증 모듈 (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) 읽기 / 쓰기 쿠키를 사용 하 여.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.CookieHandler>
